</md></sn><sn><md>#### Greek Literature

:::.row
:::.col-9 .col-md-10
The ++blind Greek epic poet++ `Homer` composed the great epics `Iliad` and `Odyssey` based on ancient stories that are thousands of years old. He is often called the `blind bard`. 
:::
