The most popular ++playwright++ of Greece was `Aeschylus`. His two famous plays are `Prometheus Bound` and `Agamemnon`. 
:::
:::


:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-9
The playwright `Sophocles` wrote more than a *hundred plays**, among which the most popular are 
`Antigone` and `Electra`. `Sophocles` famous tragedy is `Oedipus Rex`. <br>
`Euripides` was another prominent classical Greek ++playwright++. His notable play is `Orestes`.
