</md></sn><sn><md>#### Science

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
- Greek scientists were the first to `draw maps of the world`. The Greek philosopher `Anaximander` was the first to ++create a map of the Earth++.
- They were also among the first to prove that the `Earth is a planet and rotates on its own axis`. - The famous Greek mathematician `Pythagoras` was born in the 6th century BCE.
- In the 5th century BCE, the scientist `Anaxagoras` was born. 
- The physician `Hippocrates` also gained great fame for his contributions to ++medicine++.
:::

