</md></sn><sn><md>#### Sports

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-8
The `Olympic Games` were ++first introduced in Greece++ in 776 BCE. These competitions were `held every four years`. Athletes from different city-states participated in the games. Through these games, cultural unity developed among the Greeks, replacing hostility with cooperation.
